Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}即便一切 天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:47.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}唯有那件 唯有那件
