Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.70,0:00:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是按着以前的习惯在活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.59,0:00:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外出工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.82,0:00:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.19,0:00:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅是重复着身体已经记住了的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.81,0:00:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直过着这样的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛折磨自己一样一直工作着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了忘记那一切 不顾一切地工作着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈崎君 今天就到这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 马上就做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很感谢你帮我做了不少东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你这样工作小心身体吃不消哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连盂兰盆节也没休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.28,0:01:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我是因为喜欢才在干的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.97,0:01:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不偶尔休息一下的话 官厅会来啰唆的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.97,0:01:10.17,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：日本法律对劳动时间有规定，但执行不严格，多为警告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作结束后的时间和公休日过得很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅是为了打发时间而把钱花掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是投身现实的话 感觉一切都会坍塌下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.71,0:01:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这个小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.08,0:01:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是除了这个小镇也没有别处可去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛如行尸走肉般地活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也不愿去想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要把一切都忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为一切都是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与她的邂逅 交往 结婚 生子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为这一切的一切都是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果通过发自内心的希望能使这些破烂成型的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我一个人无法办到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起伤心的事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界很让人悲伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快这里就会变成一片雪白了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:05:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我动不了了的话 你就会变得孤单一人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安 朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 打搅你休息了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我一个人来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屋里有点乱 我收拾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还真是热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可不行哦 偶尔也得出去透透气才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 芳野先生也经常这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这么热的天一个人出门也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那跟我约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 忽然之间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶尔也想和年轻人约约会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么不用找我 找其他人也行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也既帅又温柔 是我最中意的类型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还总依靠着早苗阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变化…好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不常来车站这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不常来这边的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个夏天 朋也你能抽出个连休吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:07:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司那边还总说我该去休息一下了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要不要出去玩玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我们俩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真叫人心跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这次我们大家一起出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 快点来喝果汁啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以这样哦 会打搅到别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧 秋生也好久没能和朋也喝上一杯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧 好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是早苗 旅行的事考虑好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个 还没想好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我一会儿再打给你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么催得这么紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗阿姨 我败给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你答应了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 下周我会去向公司请假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算上周日 凑成四连休
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我很迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这个时候再拒绝的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像背叛了早苗阿姨似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就把一切都推给她了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有急事 我和秋生一起出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的事情就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不用这么紧张 出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗阿姨和大叔都出去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是都说了吗 早苗阿姨不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿秋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.97,0:11:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们临走时没对你交代什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不可能 因为早苗阿姨和大叔都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说你想一个人去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和早苗和阿秋一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是什么状况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这五年间 我把汐完全推给了早苗阿姨和大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连幼儿园的入园典礼和七五三节都无视 一直工作着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:16.85,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七五三节：男孩三岁、五岁或女孩三岁、七岁时\N在11月15日去神社参拜,祈求健康成长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然早苗阿姨有时会把汐带到我那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我都没怎么正眼看过她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想躲起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就看见了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这边来 别站在那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:13:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想呢 大叔和早苗阿姨大概晚上就会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天就乖乖等着吧 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等大叔和早苗阿姨回来后就能去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你就一个人玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去像个男孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你跑得那么快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去好像没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后要小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在玩这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:14:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉到地上的时候摔坏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小乌龟好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有粘合剂的话应该能修好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着 我去把它粘好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还有点裂痕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不是很显眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在它干之前不要去动它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然轮子也会被粘住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她听懂我说的话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:14:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你把这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过在它干之前不要动它的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个轮子已经动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经修不好了 放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 要扔掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么想吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:15:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的话 我就随便买了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 冈崎先生 好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 您好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 小汐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和爸爸出来买东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们现在是分开住的吧 也真难为你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个大男人 要自己把小孩拉扯大是很辛苦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你们时常有见面的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 偶尔会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不见面的话会很寂寞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 毕竟是父女嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说 说的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么小汐 拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 你自己会吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是胡椒的关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 没这个的话就不能叫炒饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐着吃下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 早苗阿姨没对你说过不可以挑食的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃早苗做的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就别吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没胡椒就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没胡椒的话会很难吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白米饭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白米饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只吃白米饭就行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话我倒省事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把炒饭当做白米饭的菜 真是奇怪的菜单
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有菜的话 就好像我是在虐待你似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.99,0:18:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拌饭料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不会回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是大的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用每次都来向我炫耀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能一个人办到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想去旅行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们两个人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意吗 和我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗阿姨和大叔都不在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:21:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他们都不回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 他们都不回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就我们两个人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有忘带东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门窗锁好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.37,0:21:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前每次见到汐的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是会有早苗阿姨或者大叔在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们像这样两个人单独在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.19,0:21:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从汐诞生之后 这五年以来还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.03,0:22:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将前往哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.86,0:23:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.14,0:23:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微考虑一下周围的人好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.74,0:23:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.55,0:23:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.87,0:23:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊 想上厕所的话先说一声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.56,0:23:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
